text.__SUMMARY__: Psychotria foetens is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Jamaica.
text.Sources: World Conservation Monitoring Centre (1998). "Psychotria foetens". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T33866A9815785. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33866A9815785.en. Retrieved 16 December 2017.
